README
------

This template has comprehensive checks to monitor the health of the swiftstack Object, Account, Proxy and Container servers

This template was modelled similar to the one provided in nagios for swiftstack monitoring

Please look at the below link for more details

https://www.swiftstack.com/docs/integration/nagios/nagios_plugin_scripts.html
https://www.swiftstack.com/docs/integration/nagios/node_setup.html

The checks include
* swift-account-auditor checks
* swift-account-replicator checks
* swift-account-server checks
* swift-container-auditor checks
* swift-container-replicator checks
* swift-container-server checks
* swift-container-updater checks
* swift-object-auditor checks
* swift-object-replicator checks
* swift-object-server checks
* swift-object-updater checks

swift check back-end daemon sweep time account-auditor
swift check back-end daemon sweep time account-reaper
swift check back-end daemon sweep time account-replicator
swift check back-end daemon sweep time container-auditor
swift check back-end daemon sweep time container-replicator
swift check back-end daemon sweep time container-updater
swift check back-end daemon sweep time object-auditor
swift check back-end daemon sweep time object-replicator
swift check back-end daemon sweep time object-updater
swift check background daemon account-auditor
swift check background daemon account-reaper
swift check background daemon account-replicator
swift check background daemon container-auditor
swift check background daemon container-replicator
swift check background daemon container-updater
swift check background daemon object-auditor
swift check background daemon object-replicator
swift check background daemon object-updater
swift check drives mounted
swift check drive utilization

and triggers for all the above


